                      ],
                      "text": "剧情预告-「人间至味」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/7caca68a51e7ac54570df4a2b11efd75_7285620431025300404.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2021年10月2日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "年岁一箸，山海一壶。阅古话今，几度春秋。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "炊烟喜乐，柴米朝暮。纤云逐月，尘世系舟。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "剧情预告-「神女劈观」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/c7c89b91a563baec537660234250afd6_3522477360373666995.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年1月6日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "道仙缘奇谈，物是人非，疏却千丝怨愁。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "歌巾帼英姿，再添新话，重入万家灯火。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "飞彩镌流年活动过场动画「岁华流彩」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/21da0584c68f1fc3b166df576240cd2c_7831080046714666114.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年1月31日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "火树银花，散漫天飞星，迎万象似锦。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "荣辉彩华，凝万千心愿，祝山月常新。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "角色展示-「瑶瑶：仙桂莹澈」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/2913894fe26a62b006d8856ba04c7c20_8178851126650009508.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2023年1月16日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "瑶瑶对其他人的关心，可不会因为对方的身分有所改变。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "无论是师父、长辈，还是玩伴、过客，都有机会体验到她的无微不至。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "请不要嫌弃瑶瑶的多话，毕竟她心中饱含的热忱关怀，可能比她说的话还要多呢。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "磬弦奏华夜活动过场动画-「虹歌灯宴」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/302104f08566c84d9702f4868938fffe_5287601238792006253.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2023年1月21日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "新岁新象，挚友挚愿。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "在这华彩映照的夜晚，璃月港内不止有霄灯，还有融汇万籁的仙乐。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "剧情预告-「余音萦心」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/157749474/7cca2be08e92fd6268d1fe9478f14c74_4229130187471243170.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2023年1月21日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "过眼云烟，浮萍无根。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "涓涓行水，渺渺涤尘。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
